@startuml sequence_chat
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Chat Messaging Flow [L2-028]

actor "Team Member" as User
participant "Chat Page\n/teams/chat" as ChatUI
participant "API Client\nlib/api/scheduling.ts" as Client
participant "Channel Routes\n/api/scheduling/channels" as API
database "PostgreSQL\nscheduling schema" as DB

User -> ChatUI: Navigate to /teams/chat
ChatUI -> Client: getChannels()
Client -> API: GET /api/scheduling/channels
API -> DB: SELECT * FROM channels
DB --> API: channels[]
API --> Client: 200 JSON
Client --> ChatUI: Render channel list

User -> ChatUI: Select channel
ChatUI -> Client: getChannelMessages(channelId)
Client -> API: GET /channels/[id]/messages
API -> DB: SELECT * FROM channel_messages\nWHERE channel_id = ?
DB --> API: messages[]
API --> Client: 200 JSON
Client --> ChatUI: Render messages

User -> ChatUI: Type message + press Enter
note right of ChatUI: Send disabled if\ninput is empty
ChatUI -> Client: sendMessage(channelId, { senderId, content })
Client -> API: POST /channels/[id]/messages
API -> DB: INSERT INTO channel_messages
DB --> API: new message
API --> Client: 201 Created
Client --> ChatUI: Append message to list

@enduml
